metadata.name: Summer Table
metadata.description:
2022 - Procreate pencil 6B on pixel canvas; 3000 x 3000 px JPG

Who is sitting at this table? Four friends: light, shadow, coolness and colour.
What are they speaking about? Fortune and future.
Are they bored? No, they are too lazy to be bored and laziness and slowness are their perfect match.
Are they leaving the table eventually? No, they cannot live one without the others.
